@startuml Async External Retrieval Flow

title Use Case 4 - Async External Online Retrieval and Late Delivery

autonumber
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 25
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ResponseMessageBelowArrow true

actor Lawyer
participant "REST API" as API
participant "Text Check Service" as TextService
participant "Async Job Queue" as Queue
participant "External Online Search Worker" as Worker
participant "External Online Sources" as Sources
participant "Result Delivery Service" as Delivery

Lawyer -> API: Submit naming check request
API -> API: Orchestrate workflow
API -> API: Normalize naming input
API -> TextService: Run text-only internal search with canonical input
TextService --> API: Top-200 internal results ready
API --> Lawyer: Return Top-200 internal results (fast)

API -> Queue: Create async external retrieval job
Queue --> Worker: Deliver async job
Worker -> Sources: Search external online sources
Sources --> Worker: External candidate set
Worker -> Worker: Rank Top-200 external results
Worker -> Delivery: External results ready
Delivery --> API: Top-200 external results (later)
API --> Lawyer: Deliver Top-200 external results (later)

@enduml

